rComments: Clearly cares a lot about his students. The class wasn't on the most engaging material, but he threw in enough jokes and was helpful enough to make it a decent experience. Outrageously detailed slides that he puts online. Someone asked the dumbest question I've ever heard in a university setting in this class, and he wasn't condescending intheleast

Possibly the worst philosophy prof I have ever had in my four years of college. Unclear, disorganized, unsure of material and mumbles a lot. Bad lecture slides. Makes me want to pull out my hair and cry everytime I go to lecture. To be fair, he seems like a bright guy and I am sure he is - he just needs to work on his teaching.
